('### 5.3. Acreditación de la estancia de 5 meses
La forma principal de acreditar la estancia es el **padrón histórico**. Si tienes padrón, solícitalo lo antes posible, ya que las citas son difíciles de conseguir. **¡Empieza a pedir cita ya!** Para familias se necesita el **padrón de convivencia histórico**, aún más difícil de obtener.', '[-0.005934629,0.014539908,0.025399193,-0.04735439,0.009770503,0.0109079,0.01739249,0.00084145885,0.011967699,0.002831639,-0.015525006,-0.013546183,-0.014701202,0.020726567,0.122876644,0.011924306,-0.008042337,0.017648505,-0.0071786214,-0.012922264,0.019508254,0.008137666,-0.015812056,-0.020585522,-0.005631843,0.014239606,0.022276612,0.011273764,0.032358903,-0.01706094,-0.0002575298,0.02736573,-0.019429225,0.024003156,-0.007566326,0.023301503,0.0042916844,0.0061255754,0.00683659,0.0112865865,0.011435603,-0.0071429634,-0.011535908,-0.0049778386,0.009143236,-0.013080222,-0.0019648452,-0.008971969,-0.012397503,0.0014965934,0.0071039884,-0.0062387437,-0.022823913,-0.18609795,-0.0055031297,-0.031873643,-0.008185317,0.017617598,0.00091309624,-0.021181798,-0.03271955,0.023094164,-0.0050394754,0.0035346437,0.026635613,0.010854425,0.0155365765,0.03896541,0.00082762865,-0.021148594,-0.0111966245,0.0076536983,0.006262447,-0.030650022,0.010337242,-0.024851087,-0.005995926,0.009406831,-0.011017879,0.004729917,0.00026946276,-0.0014181002,0.0024568585,-0.0062011546,0.027768409,-0.01642712,0.001203075,0.00932905,-0.01127294,0.0111321295,-0.0011743021,0.017988551,0.00058784295,-0.018371288,0.02850462,0.00041654822,-0.0067557096,-0.00811508,-0.027906565,-0.024981603,-0.008648863,-0.014868246,-0.004870982,0.019384116,0.013255594,-0.039398573,-0.003249364,0.0067778486,-0.007827616,0.010219831,0.007194291,-0.00086467224,-0.0056552053,0.022945713,0.0055151912,-0.18113987,-0.005389643,0.027872894,-0.005676525,-0.03143996,-0.0015494056,0.012548918,-0.0008556482,-0.0076184985,0.01062982,-0.0070726955,0.009389068,-0.02579518,-0.004862368,-0.0191275,-0.009901027,-0.016692366,0.008802837,0.0068767834,-0.00984