('> [!WARNING]
> **Sobre el informe de vulnerabilidad:** Aunque la situación administrativa irregular se presume vulnerable, **Regularización Ya recomienda intentar obtener el certificado igualmente**. Si la administración lo requiere posteriormente, solo dará un plazo de **10 días hábiles** para aportarlo. Es mejor tenerlo preparado que arriesgarse a no poder conseguirlo en ese plazo. El modelo de certificado de vulnerabilidad se puede descargar aquí: https://inclusion.gob.es/documents/20121/7817425/Modelo%20de%20certificado%20de%20vulnerabilidad.pdf', '[-0.013221924,-0.0072320024,0.0050820047,-0.060637835,0.022214005,0.0133527825,0.025173025,-0.0073441286,0.006565687,-0.0023888322,-0.013241773,-0.0034294892,-0.0011040268,0.033187084,0.1214915,0.0047479453,-0.0074243597,0.012263907,-0.00070869434,-0.011091681,0.02749545,-0.005800658,-0.033197813,0.0044959635,-0.011589635,0.016872544,0.030856613,0.02574764,0.0223237,-0.0052096215,0.0039257687,0.01158465,0.0011499187,0.02514582,-0.0021616544,0.010693506,-0.0030161247,-0.011980624,-0.0210826,-0.006073193,0.018643863,0.019030355,-0.010291221,-0.004409467,0.011761468,-0.021111412,-0.0063842745,-0.0007251462,-0.022096574,0.018718293,0.0056528384,-0.03181273,-0.021530708,-0.16107987,0.0058253133,-0.0047735246,-0.016595282,-0.010700763,0.010953077,-0.017036086,-0.037404183,0.038669236,0.0013702745,-0.011659004,-0.007154202,-0.015995663,0.02542716,0.011958078,0.0022980142,-0.024688628,-0.0030244193,-0.020605229,0.0038792798,-0.01738019,0.018773481,-0.01156753,-0.0070699244,0.008229907,-0.019549001,-0.0018047652,-0.011747096,0.0036622111,0.008134517,-0.0058734408,0.018234948,0.0047772313,0.021459522,0.029849863,-0.0032708377,0.017872194,0.007821962,0.03159083,-0.001877177,-0.027827179,0.021033945,-0.006470408,0.005590588,0.006225492,4.2696247e-05,-0.014387762,-0.024198743,-0.0085844025,-0.024249533,0.012571286,0.038653627,-0.025219051,-0.015465744,-0.0038953552,0.020562982,0.011321563,-0.008950822,0.007557436,-0.010365692,0.027212901,0.005