('### 12.3. Obtener el número de Seguridad Social
**Posibles dificultades:**
En la práctica, para autentificarte telemáticamente necesitas la tarjeta vigente, lo que a veces genera "un laberinto" hasta que te dejan hacerlo con la cara del pasaporte. El movimiento está trabajando para facilitar estos mecanismos y preparar instrucciones claras (*"vale, tienes que decir tal, tal, tal, y a la tercera ya la tienes"*).', '[-0.010898248,-0.0026730588,0.00060544675,-0.04556482,0.004148551,0.011436348,0.014034888,0.01955553,0.008131648,-0.0029411332,-0.008334054,0.032133374,0.02248229,0.03214709,0.13819279,0.0095358435,0.010747417,0.017028062,-0.010406799,-0.022029426,0.037340146,-0.0021512022,-0.03362971,-0.00917844,-0.0021188133,0.0022026116,0.025817607,0.009586912,0.040874824,-0.025954733,0.007925395,0.015189912,0.005567679,0.041603554,-0.037374474,0.01565995,0.009750071,-0.028610671,-0.0048777023,0.013061225,0.023614442,-0.0037693812,0.0021551077,-0.007260407,0.017326314,-0.005903927,-0.0012970176,-0.014427352,0.003024373,0.0012387009,-0.00016796842,0.02023772,-0.04061242,-0.16805875,0.013978428,-0.028603708,0.011224749,0.011233,-0.0037582866,-0.027417038,-0.0333112,0.022064567,-0.0098281475,-0.008427802,0.0073267464,0.0037267716,0.03614138,0.03216283,-0.002752556,-0.021785937,-0.008183788,-0.010769682,-0.013664966,-0.033109665,0.00490658,-0.016115585,-0.009624007,0.012874586,0.0006511455,-0.0016113756,-0.029490676,-0.005475774,-0.0066020736,-0.0049796044,0.021043478,-0.020601803,0.025742475,0.013828472,-0.014462176,0.010659441,0.0046115858,0.02295382,0.0046862643,-0.025706707,0.01842971,-0.0040799063,-0.017678926,0.010495641,0.0015828056,-0.0048188977,-0.011985975,-0.018303141,0.0010796341,0.0031549598,0.01701841,-0.041790824,-0.018230282,0.0053735147,0.00037010937,-0.00055483123,-0.007280443,0.003767165,-0.00024421184,0.020457009,0.012682251,-0.16761716,-0.0062573217,0.008828453,-0.006794526,-0.00291026,0.018107597,0.0067238696,0.00018635837,0.012817871,0.002564767,0.0041102176,0.016872872,-0.030300265,-0.003388211,-0.00011332855,0.0065419995,-