('### 13.15. Multa por estancia irregular
**Perfil:** Persona en proceso de regularización a quien se le ha aplicado una multa por estancia irregular.
**Pregunta:** "Esta mañana me aplicaron una multa por estancia irregular. ¿Afectará eso a mi proceso de regularización extraordinaria?"
**Respuesta:** **NO debería afectar.**
**Explicación:** El texto previsto indica que los procedimientos de expulsión o devolución iniciados por estancia irregular quedarán **archivados automáticamente** una vez que se conceda la autorización de residencia. La multa no bloquea la solicitud ni la resolución.', '[0.0057649906,0.02701903,0.025392268,-0.06290275,0.018857064,0.02272704,0.01227585,0.009062484,0.010057433,-0.011449185,0.00077017787,0.0108322315,0.0029896477,0.019861916,0.11390839,0.01230515,0.011255128,0.013458438,0.005891909,-0.008983262,0.026043335,0.013400415,-0.025878139,-0.0013083544,-0.03729768,0.016366387,0.040612027,0.016949892,0.041337114,-0.025001468,-0.0155760255,0.023310473,-0.00041330542,0.024761576,-0.022189263,0.038972355,-0.00429326,0.007561448,-0.0015347456,-0.0086170705,0.0024127641,-0.0051055024,-0.013637799,0.007057161,0.025873944,-0.007777159,-0.010674139,-0.031548202,-0.031404488,0.022497403,-0.0064615984,-0.0066657527,-0.044342883,-0.16413224,0.014983011,-0.008052513,-0.00677542,0.00052979804,0.007107222,-0.0122222155,-0.028859593,0.035148323,-0.004180222,-0.02202848,0.010493541,0.008944235,-0.0038602394,0.024031641,-0.002538209,-0.015139656,0.017247504,-0.004725876,-0.0024083164,-0.0049291286,0.027401717,-0.019549893,0.01904664,0.01705063,-0.018014582,0.0052106325,0.007892058,0.02541329,0.0045234542,-0.028127324,0.017957035,0.0044740764,0.016005872,0.00997942,-0.01628092,0.016771363,0.0074577145,0.006797345,-0.00017115373,-0.020331057,-0.0125015965,0.0023759867,-0.0010092218,0.017455878,-0.00019245016,-0.039828185,-0.0113538075,-0.012020568,0.008652098,0.025037125,0.03034343,-0.021294419,0.005960359,0.020394217,-0.0046120975,-0.017039597,0.009388176,-0.012805817,-0.0006852535,0.0160055,0.009356692,-0.17663564,0.049728412,0.0005458641,-0.009159373,-0.027929615,0.006454913,0.03201707,0.0075862035,0.008705998,-0.013400722,-0.02640991,0.0012180138,-0.00931147,0.0014140687,-0.003870712,0.012868872,-0.0044027977,0.011671964,0.0020622236,-0.02663978,0.019759264,-0.021080306,-0.0