: null, "source": "Manual_Regularizacion_Extraordinaria.md", "section": "MANUAL SOBRE LA REGULARIZACI\u00d3N EXTRAORDINARIA", "subsection": "13. Casu\u00edsticas y ejemplos pr\u00e1cticos", "subsubsection": "13.15. Multa por estancia irregular"}'),
('### 13.16. ¿Hay que esperar a que el Congreso vote?
**Perfil:** Persona que ha visto noticias sobre intentos parlamentarios de enmendar o frenar la regularización.
**Pregunta:** "He visto que en el Congreso se está intentando enmendar o frenar la regularización. ¿Debemos esperar a que se vote antes de conseguir los documentos?"
**Respuesta:** **NO. No depende del Congreso.**
**Explicación:** Esta regularización se aprueba mediante un **Real Decreto (Reglamento)**, que es potestad exclusiva del Gobierno. Al no ser un Real Decreto-Ley, no necesita pasar por el Congreso para su convalidación ni votación. Lo que se vote en el Congreso no tiene implicación directa en este Real Decreto. **El RD 316/2026 ya ha sido publicado en el BOE y está en vigor desde el 16 de abril de 2026.**', '[0.0007601822,0.0074134334,0.0279461,-0.07084795,0.015265866,0.023558041,0.020821229,0.027766064,-0.008948306,-0.014921274,-0.019907331,-0.015899006,-0.0005722947,0.023774328,0.12882183,0.014881681,0.021955613,0.021490961,-0.001614676,-0.0072418875,0.02339776,0.008484957,-0.019553015,-0.0010878502,-0.0087848855,0.009455456,0.026809528,0.009526236,0.035534926,-0.016386537,0.0056217853,0.0064286455,0.012991236,0.024070922,-0.013550611,0.013343161,-0.0032066149,-0.007288529,-0.014774913,0.008991613,-0.0059550866,-0.0042836815,-0.01749486,-0.022903068,0.037520472,0.0038109862,-0.017557606,-0.03789339,-0.020544717,0.024544442,-0.00078558293,-0.0156271,-0.031183865,-0.16305247,-0.0107226735,-0.010288923,-0.012640702,0.0065795598,0.009670269,-0.016229348,-0.037588634,0.031021373,-0.008245904,-0.00861304,0.009650444,0.0064444635,0.024280056,0.005731678,-0.0012854837,-0.021505095,-0.011911611,-0.005933819,-0.0043929517,-0.0024294243,0.01282626,-0.0094049955,0.013649548,0.017208852,-0.017993122,-0.008209826,-0.016036274,-0.010087048,-0.011416772,-0.008557663,0.019942053,-0.004126504,0.024102012,0.0063692993,0.006764329,0.009181193,-0.018770637,0.019435413,-0.010012976,-0.030326592,0.008414395,-0.012439106,0.004374486,0.0012623925,-0.00506852,-0.002502453,-0.025030896,0.002420566,0.0002210327,0.0057748393,0.03629037,-0.011134712,0.0135270795,0.016814565,-0.006360786,0.005614421,-0.011737171,-0.01951221,0.0065293433,0.007805713,-0.0005938628,-0.16654661,0.013203702,0.012795045,-0.005666359,-0.026508383,0.003946563,0.009638598,-0.011189397,-0.00017911862,0.006204067,-0.002700